26:07.120 --> 26:09.714
Oh, no. My plucky idealist.

26:10.720 --> 26:12.756
So, gentlemen, how's business?

26:12.960 --> 26:14.871
Not bad, Raymond.
Business is not bad.

26:15.080 --> 26:16.399
