26:16.600 --> 26:17.874
Any better and you guys
are gonna have

26:18.080 --> 26:19.479
more assets than
the European Union.

26:19.680 --> 26:20.669
Don't we already?

26:21.120 --> 26:24.669
Every great society,
every great civilization,

26:24.880 --> 26:26.836
always anchored by a great navy.

26:27.040 --> 26:28.598
- Congressman Shaw.
- Thanks very much.

26:28.800 --> 26:31.553
Nice to see you, Bob.
Thanks for coming.

26:32.600 --> 26:33.715
Congressman.

26:36.320 --> 26:38.038
Ben Marco.

26:38.240 --> 26:40.800
I know. Hello, captain.

26:41.480 --> 26:42.833
How you doing?

26:43.040 --> 26:45.713
- I need to talk to you.
- Okay.

26:46.040 --> 26:48.395
Oh, my God, Raymond,
it's been so many years.

26:48.600 --> 26:49.999
- And?
- And I've been married,

26:50.200 --> 26:51.315
- I've been divorced.
- Yeah.

26:51.520 --> 26:53.397
Well, you may have noticed
I've changed a bit myself.

26:53.600 --> 26:57.070
No. No, that's not...
No, yes, I have noticed.

26:57.280 --> 27:01.068
I see. It's great.
Congratulations.

27:01.280 --> 27:02.713
My feelings haven't, though.

27:05.160 --> 27:07.469
Changed, I mean.

27:09.120 --> 27:12.271
What feelings? What?

27:13.400 --> 27:15.630
Jocelyn, I have never
stopped wondering

27:15.840 --> 27:18.957
how things might have turned out
between us

27:19.160 --> 27:21.674
- if my mother hadn't...
- Raymond.

27:21.880 --> 27:24.269
Raymond, people can't just
rewrite their lives.

27:26.360 --> 27:28.999
I haven't had a relationship...

27:29.200 --> 27:31.475
...of any consequence
since we stopped seeing each other.

27:31.680 --> 27:34.035
Doesn't that say something to you?

27:34.840 --> 27:37.559
Yeah, that...

27:37.760 --> 27:41.196
That you must be just about
the loneliest person on this earth.

27:42.080 --> 27:45.550
Raymond, we were kids then. It must
have been, what, 15 years ago?

27:45.760 --> 27:46.829
It was sweet, but...

27:47.680 --> 27:48.999
Joce.

27:49.800 --> 27:52.268
Yeah. I have to go.

27:52.960 --> 27:55.474
- Yeah.
- Best of luck with the campaign.

27:56.160 --> 27:57.149
Thank you.

28:01.280 --> 28:02.679
Joce...

28:02.880 --> 28:05.314
Sergeant Raymond Shaw.

28:09.280 --> 28:11.316
I wanna talk to you too.

28:13.560 --> 28:14.709
- Not now.
- Excuse me, sir.

28:14.920 --> 28:16.353
I mean, I know you're busy,
congressman...

28:16.560 --> 28:18.357
- Don't touch me.
- I'm sorry.

28:18.560 --> 28:21.393
I'm sorry, it's just that, well...

28:21.600 --> 28:23.477
Don't ever touch me.

28:27.280 --> 28:29.840
Hello, major.
Have you tried the Pad Thai?

28:30.080 --> 28:32.594
I'm told it rules.

28:40.320 --> 28:42.276
<i>What were you hoping</i>
<i>Congressman Shaw would say?</i>

28:42.680 --> 28:44.318
I don't know, sir.

28:45.400 --> 28:49.359
It's not so much what he said
or didn't say, it was more of his...

28:49.560 --> 28:51.118
...attitude, his demeanor.

28:51.600 --> 28:52.794
Are you taking your meds?

28:53.000 --> 28:55.116
Lieutenant Colonel Howard,
with all due respect,

28:55.320 --> 28:57.197
I've had over a dozen years
of experts telling me

28:57.400 --> 29:00.039
that I have Gulf War Syndrome,
I have post-traumatic stress disorder

29:00.240 --> 29:03.312
and every other mood disorder
that you can name.

29:03.520 --> 29:06.796
In those 12 years,
I've been a good soldier.

29:07.000 --> 29:09.912
And I've denied what
every nerve ending in my body

29:10.120 --> 29:11.792
is telling me is more real than not.

29:12.000 --> 29:14.195
I've had one dream,
not variations on a dream,

29:14.400 --> 29:15.913
the same dream.
Night after night...

29:16.120 --> 29:19.032
No. No. I'm sorry.

29:19.240 --> 29:21.595
You're saying that an entire squad
of U.S. Army soldiers

29:21.800 --> 29:23.631
was hypnotized into believing
that Raymond Shaw

29:23.840 --> 29:25.353
deserved the Medal of Honor.

29:25.640 --> 29:28.154
And that somehow,
thanks to your dream,

29:28.360 --> 29:30.794
you're the only one
who knows the truth.

29:31.520 --> 29:34.432
Major Marco, you will stay clear
of Congressman Shaw.

29:39.760 --> 29:42.513
And you are to resume
your medication.

29:42.720 --> 29:44.517
That is an order.

29:44.720 --> 29:46.199
That will be all, major.

