32:34.240 --> 32:35.559
Am I that predictable?

32:35.840 --> 32:37.671
You have no idea.

32:37.920 --> 32:40.514
I'm calling to compliment you,
Mr. Grumpy.

32:40.720 --> 32:43.553
I thought you were
magnificent tonight.

32:43.800 --> 32:46.598
And so did all the network
campaign experts.

32:47.120 --> 32:50.510
<i>And that compassionate</i>
<i>vigilance thing</i>

32:50.720 --> 32:53.359
<i>is working quite well for you.</i>

32:54.040 --> 32:56.918
- I might have to convert.
- I happen to believe in it.

32:57.120 --> 32:58.519
<i>Oh, yes, of course you do.</i>

32:58.720 --> 33:00.392
<i>- Now, Raymond...</i>
- Good night, Mother.

33:00.920 --> 33:03.150
<i>Raymond? What? No, wait, wait.</i>

33:04.720 --> 33:06.836
- Hang on a second.
<i>- What? Raymond?</i>

33:07.320 --> 33:08.514
Are you there?

33:11.080 --> 33:12.433
