33:12.800 --> 33:14.552
<i>Sergeant Shaw?</i>

33:14.960 --> 33:16.598
Who is this?

33:17.280 --> 33:20.272
<i>- Sergeant Raymond Shaw?</i>
- Yes.

33:20.600 --> 33:23.068
<i>Raymond Prentiss Shaw?</i>

33:28.120 --> 33:29.553
