33:29.840 --> 33:31.114
<i>Listen.</i>

33:31.680 --> 33:33.716
<i>Go to the bedroom of your suite.</i>

33:34.320 --> 33:36.914
<i>Enter the hallway there.</i>

33:37.120 --> 33:40.556
<i>Go to the end and open the closet.</i>

34:08.639 --> 34:10.755
